Class ApproverComment

  • java.lang.Object
    • cmput301w15t07.TravelTracker.model.ApproverComment

  • public class ApproverComment
extends java.lang.Object
    Model class for the Approver Comment. Setters are not exposed - object attributes are set at construction time. This is so that mutations must be made at the Claim for observer notification and cache dirtying.

    ryant26, colp
